<p>于晓光受命担任扶贫书记</p>
<p>城市干部融入难</p>
<p><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201123/f77b0c66974746d1b857cdc18ff6ab71.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
